com.intel.icecp.core.security

Class SecurityServices<I,T extends SecurityService<I>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.icecp.core.security.SecurityServices<I,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - Security service id type parameter
    T - Service type (subclass of SecurityService) service

    public class SecurityServices<I,T extends SecurityService<I>>
extends Object
    Abstract class that provides basic service loading functionalities for security services extending SecurityService. Services are loaded using Java ServiceLoader.
